    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Distinctive badges, devices, or marks bearing a crest, heraldic bearing, coat of arms, or other mark worn by a person or company or attached to property, particularly such devices intended to denote ownership of property or affiliation of retainers to a noble house, whether the retainers bore arms or not.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
